text: Sybra quadriplagiata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Breuning in 1939. It is known from Australia.BioLib.cz - Sybra quadriplagiata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== quadriplagiata Category:Beetles described in 1939
